title: Citizen Eco-Drive WDR Mens Watch CA4190-54E - Overview
description:
Citizen Eco-Drive WDR Silver Tone Stainless Steel Mens Watch - http://www.abt.com/product/88510/Citizen-CA419054E.html

A powerful stainless steel case with a sleek black dial and powerful red accents make this watch the perfect accessory for any mans wardrobe. Featuring 1/5-second chronograph measuring up to 60 minutes 12/24-hour time and date.

Features:
• Movement: Eco-Drive B620
• Functions: 1/5 Second Chronograph 3 Hand 12/24-Hour Time
• Band: Silver-Tone Stainless Steel Bracelet Fold Over Clasp
• Case Size: 45mm
• Case Material: Silver-Tone Stainless Steel
• Dial: Red Accented Dial
• Crystal: Mineral Crystal
• Water Resistance: WR100/10Bar/333ft Swimming Showering & Snorkeling
